      "content": "That's a start, but it feels a little bit like a caricature. In reality, these guys were community leaders and business owners, so they probably wouldn't be so overt about being \"troublemakers\" right away—it would be more about \"tradition\" and \"order.\" Can you make it more subtle? Maybe show them talking about how the \"natural order\" of the town is being threatened and they need to take \"decisive action\" to protect their way of life, without sounding like cartoon villains. I want to capture that sense of them thinking they are actually doing the right thing for the community.",
